exrest: Rome Newswire was a local online daily newspaper of Rome, Georgia, United States. It is owned by Seven Hills Media, LLC. It was established as a daily news blog by local radio personality Jerry Duke and quickly grew to become one of the leading news sites in the Northwest Georgia region.
